[["wrb.fr",null,"[null,[\"c_c670d3afc2ffa77c\",\"r_181e47f974fd9e91\"],null,null,[[\"rc_583a6122517a71fe\",[\"\\u003ctool_call\\u003e{\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec_command\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"cmd\\\":\\\"git status --short; cargo test --lib one_click_quantity || cargo test || true\\\",\\\"workdir\\\":\\\"/home/riley/spotlessbinco\\\",\\\"yield_time_ms\\\":30000,\\\"max_output_tokens\\\":12000}}\\u003c/tool_call\\u003e\\n\\u003ctool_call\\u003e{\\\"name\\\":\\\"update_goal\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\"}}\\u003c/tool_call\\u003e\\nI've simplified the `window_cleaning_side_sell` component to rely strictly on exact pane count while keeping server-authoritative one-click pricing completely intact.\\n\\n## Summary of Changes\\n\\n* **Template \\u0026 Component UI (`_window_cleaning_side_sell.html.tera`)**:\\n  * Removed all house-size selection buttons (`Small`, `Medium`, `Large`, `Extra Large`).\\n  * Simplified the interface to a single exact pane-count numeric input (`min\\u003d\\\"1\\\" max\\u003d\\\"200\\\"`).\\n  * Direct calculations now update the running total directly from pane count and catalog unit price.\\n\\n* **Client Upsell Script (`static/js/funnel-upsell.js`)**:\\n  * Stripped house-size dataset attributes (`selectedSize`, `houseSize`).\\n  * Standardized payload generation for `window_cleaning_side_sell` to pass `quantity` (exact pane count) directly to the server checkout endpoint.\\n\\n* **Server Validation \\u0026 Controller Logic (`one_click_quantity.rs` \\u0026 `one_click_upsell.rs`)**:\\n  * Updated `validate_quantity` to validate per-pane quantity pricing (`1..\\u003d200`) without requiring or checking house-size selections.\\n  * Preserved server-side catalog unit price lookup and multiplication (`unit_amount_cents * quantity`) to prevent client-side amount tampering.\\n  * Cleaned up purchase tracking/idempotency keys to reflect the simplified quantity structure.\\n\\n* **Schemas \\u0026 Admin Interfaces**:\\n  * Updated `windowCleaningSideSellSchema` default descriptions and form helpers to guide users to input pane count.\\n  * Added a database migration (`20260722010000-window-cleaning-side-sell-disclaimer`) to align existing step components and template descriptions with the simplified exact pane-count copy.\"],null,null,null,null,null,null,[1],\"en\",null,null,[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[]],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[]]],[\"Lavon, TX, USA\",\"SWML_DESCRIPTION_FROM_YOUR_INTERNET_ADDRESS\",false,null,\"//www.google.com/maps/vt/data\\u003dkxGNWLMWtoBa-79WrzrBHe0msgrD3u6d6Yqnr2FIjayFJXag_tNga-2qoxT2Xmw6MBTWZQFb19F8Lis3Oi5QmnUV6k7yx0BBUBLBdHg-rxuZKxRruEKBk4l2xi9nIyZGMVLzymnJW0cP-Yf1wALsNUPBWZH7yFfJo1MszhNHn4xfusgUM8gOuvo68iHstoCS\"],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,false,null,null,null,null,\"en\",null,null,null,true,null,null,[[[[null,[null,0,\"\\u003ctool_call\\u003e{\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec_command\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"cmd\\\":\\\"git status --short; cargo test --lib one_click_quantity || cargo test || true\\\",\\\"workdir\\\":\\\"/home/riley/spotlessbinco\\\",\\\"yield_time_ms\\\":30000,\\\"max_output_tokens\\\":12000}}\\u003c/tool_call\\u003e\\n\\u003ctool_call\\u003e{\\\"name\\\":\\\"update_goal\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\"}}\\u003c/tool_call\\u003e\\nI've simplified the window_cleaning_side_sell component to rely strictly on exact pane count while keeping server-authoritative one-click pricing completely intact.\",[[333,358,[[null,null,null,null,3]]]]]],[null,[null,2,\"Summary of Changes\"]],[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[[[[[null,[null,0,\"Template \\u0026 Component UI (_window_cleaning_side_sell.html.tera):\",[[25,61,[[null,null,null,null,3]]],[0,62,[[null,null,null,null,2]]]]]],[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[[[[[null,[null,0,\"Removed all house-size selection buttons (Small, Medium, Lar